			<h2>Shipping Information Policy</h2>
            <h3>1. Overview</h3>
            At TONNS, we strive to deliver your orders in a timely and efficient manner. This Shipping Information Policy outlines the shipping methods, processing times, delivery times, and other important details related to shipping.
            <br><br>
            <h3>2. Shipping Destinations</h3>
            We offer shipping to the following destinations:

            Domestic (within Legoland)<br>
            International (to selected countries)<br>
            Please note that some products may have restrictions on delivery to certain regions or countries due to legal or logistical reasons. If your order cannot be shipped to your location, you will be notified at checkout.
            <br><br>
            <h3>3. Shipping Methods & Costs</h3>
            <h5>3.1 Shipping Methods</h5>
            We offer the following shipping methods:<br>

            Standard Shipping: Estimated delivery within 7 business days.<br>
            Expedited Shipping: Estimated delivery within 3 business days.<br>
            Overnight Shipping: Estimated delivery by the next business day.
            <br>
            <h5>3.2 Shipping Costs</h5>
            Shipping costs are calculated based on the weight, dimensions, and destination of your order. The exact shipping charges will be displayed at checkout before you complete your purchase.<br>

            Free Shipping: We offer free standard shipping on orders over 3 within Legoland. Free shipping promotions are subject to change and may vary by region.
            <br><br>
            <h3>4. Order Processing Time</h3>
            <h5>4.1 Processing Time</h5>
            Orders are processed within 2 business days (excluding weekends and holidays) after receiving your order confirmation email. You will receive another notification when your order has shipped.
            <br>
            <h5>4.2 Delays</h5>
            Please note that processing times may be delayed during peak seasons (e.g., holidays) or due to high order volumes. We will do our best to notify you of any significant delays.
            <br><br>
            <h3>5. Delivery Time</h3>
            <h5>5.1 Estimated Delivery Time</h5>
            Estimated delivery times are based on the shipping method selected and the destination of your order. While we aim to deliver within the estimated timeframe, please note that actual delivery times may vary due to factors beyond our control, such as customs processing or carrier delays.
            <br>
            <h5>5.2 Tracking Your Order</h5>
            Once your order has shipped, you will receive a shipping confirmation email with a tracking number and link to track your order. Please allow 3 hours for the tracking information to update.
            <br><br>
            <h3>6. International Shipping</h3>
            <h5>6.1 Customs, Duties, and Taxes</h5>
            International orders may be subject to customs duties, taxes, and import fees, which are not included in our shipping charges. These charges are the responsibility of the customer and are typically collected by the carrier at the time of delivery.
            <br>
            <h5>6.2 Shipping Times</h5>
            International shipping times vary depending on the destination country and customs processing times. Estimated delivery times for international orders are typically 3 to 7 business days but may be longer.
            <br><br>
            <h3>7. Shipping Restrictions</h3>
            <h5>7.1 P.O. Boxes & APO/FPO Addresses</h5>
            We do not ship to P.O. Boxes, APO, or FPO addresses. Please provide a valid residential or commercial address at checkout.
            <br>
            <h5>7.2 Restricted Products</h5>
            Certain products may be restricted from shipping to specific locations due to regulatory or carrier restrictions. If an item in your order cannot be shipped to your location, we will notify you and provide alternative options.
            <br><br>
            <h3>8. Missing, Lost, or Damaged Packages</h3>
            <h5>8.1 Missing or Lost Packages</h5>
            If your package is marked as delivered but you have not received it, please:<br>

            Check with neighbors or other household members to see if they received the package.<br>
            Contact the carrier to inquire about the delivery.<br>
            If the package cannot be located, contact our customer service team at tonnslegostore@shop.com within 5 days of the marked delivery date.
            <br>
            <h5>8.2 Damaged Packages</h5>
            If your package arrives damaged, please take photos of the damage and contact our customer service team immediately. We will work with you to resolve the issue, whether by sending a replacement or issuing a refund.
            <br><br>
            <h3>9. Order Changes and Cancellations</h3>
            <h5>9.1 Order Changes</h5>
            If you need to make changes to your order (e.g., shipping address, item quantity), please contact us as soon as possible. We will do our best to accommodate your request, but changes may not be possible once the order has been processed or shipped.
            <br>
            <h5>9.2 Order Cancellations</h5>
            If you wish to cancel your order, please contact us immediately. Orders that have already been processed or shipped cannot be canceled, but you may be able to return the item(s) following our Return Policy.
            <br><br>
            <h3>10. Contact Us</h3>
            If you have any questions or concerns about our Shipping Information Policy, please contact us at:<br>

            TONNS Lego Store<br>
            Lego Street 123, Legoland<br>
            +9727684032<br>
            tonnslegostore@shop.com<br>

            
